name: Hiroshi Tanaka
profile_summary: This 28-year-old, straight man stands at 5'10" and is a software engineer in the technology sector. Originally from Tokyo, Japan, he now resides in Los Angeles, California. A graduate of the University of Tokyo, he is proficient in both Japanese and English. His interests include coding, hiking, anime, and traveling. As a motivated, adventurous, and independent individual, he is politically liberal and adheres to Buddhist beliefs. His relationship preference is monogamy and his aim is to have a long-term relationship. While he doesn't have children yet, he is keen to have them in the future, and he currently doesn't own any pets. A Taurus, and an ISTJ personality type, he maintains an active lifestyle and does not indulge in smoking, drinking, or any kind of drugs.
preferences_summary: The user is seeking a woman aged between 24 to 32 years, with a height range of 5'0" to 6'0". His potential partner should not have children but should want them in the future. As for lifestyle choices, his ideal partner doesn't drink, smoke, or consume marijuana and drugs, but is active in terms of exercise. He is open to dating any woman of White Caucasian, East Asian, South Asian, or Southeast Asian ethnicity. The political inclination of the partner can either be Liberal or Moderate. The user doesn't have a preference for a specific job industry or language, but values in his partner should include ambition, adventure, and motivation. Any interests are acceptable. In terms of education, his ideal partner should have at least an undergraduate degree. The user is looking for a straight woman who indulges in monogamous long term relationships.
